Description: Naruto and his allies battle an army of undead ninjas and an unexpected resurrection throws them all for a loop.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 59
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 8
Author: Kazue Kato

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates search for a legendary treasure called “One Piece.”
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 65
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Welcome to the Death Weapon Meister Academy, where students learn how to control their armaments in classes like NOT (Normally Overcome Targets) and EAT (Especially Advantaged Talent).
Title: SOUL EATER NOT!, VOL. 2
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, Ichigo chance at a normal life is disrupted.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 50
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, Ichigo is quickly regaining the powers he thought lost.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 51
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: In this reimagining of Lewis Carroll's "Alice's Adventures in Wonderland," the Cheshire Cat, disguised as a human named Boris, vies for Alice's affections.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF CLOVER: CHESHIRE CAT WALTZ, VOL. 3
Author: QuinRose

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 15
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 8
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO±VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 10
Author: Akihisa Ikeda
